    "Sustainable horticulture requires:\n",
    "- Soil health maintenance\n",
    "- Water conservation\n",
    "- Climate adaptation\n",
    "- Biodiversity support\n",
    "- Minimal chemical use\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook provides tools for environmental monitoring and management.\n",
